<DIV
CLASS="SECT1"
><H1
CLASS="SECT1"
><A
NAME="AEN75"
>3.1 Pre-installation checklist</A
></H1
>
<P
>Before installing HPF, you need to make sure that the following programs are already installed:</P
>
<P
></P
><UL
><LI
><P
>svn</P
></LI
><LI
><P
>MySQL database</P
></LI
><LI
><P
>PHP-enabled web server with gd library</P
></LI
><LI
><P
>PHP with command line interface and MySQL module</P
></LI
></UL
>
<P
>Of course, you need all the necessary software including GNU autotools and a C/C++ compiler to build HDF5 library.</P
>

<P
>The first step of using HPF is to get the HPF source codes from subversion repository.
<TABLE
BORDER="0"
BGCOLOR="#E0E0E0"
WIDTH="100%"
><TR
><TD
><PRE
CLASS="PROGRAMLISTING"
> %svn co http://svn.hdfgroup.uiuc.edu/hdf5perf</PRE
></TD
></TR
></TABLE
></P
></DIV
